<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px
      solid #dddddd; border-radius: 10px; background-color: #f9f9f9; } .header {
      font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-bottom:
      20px; } .footer { font-size: 12px; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;
      color: #888888; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>Welcome to Your E-learn Account!</div>
      <p>Dear {{name}} {{lastName}},</p>
      <p>
        Your account has been created by your tutor,
        <strong>{{tutorName}} {{tutorLastName}}</strong>.
      </p>
      <p>Please use the following credentials to log in:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</li>
        <li><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> {{temporaryPassword}}</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Kindly change your password upon first login.</p>
      <p>{{loginUrl}}</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>Your E-learn Team</p>
      <div class='footer'>
        This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>